				2025.</div><div style="margin:0 0 1em 0;">(b) Twenty-one million four hundred thirty-five thousand dollars ($21,435,000) from unallocated special funds is increased from Item 9800-001-0494 of Section 2.00 of the Budget Act of 2025.</div><div style="margin:0 0 1em 0;">(c) Eight million three hundred ninety-five thousand dollars ($8,395,000) from other unallocated nongovernmental cost funds is reduced from Item 9800-001-0988 of Section 2.00 of the Budget Act of 2025.</div></div></div><div id="s130.7239363038159495"><div><div style="margin:0 0 1em 0;"><h3 style="font-weight:bold; display:inline;">SEC. 13.</h3> This act is a bill providing for appropriations related to the Budget Bill within the meaning of subdivision (e) of Section 12 of Article IV of the California Constitution, has been identified as related to the budget in the Budget Bill, and shall take effect immediately.</div></div></div></div></div></body></html>
